{"id":79285,"title":"Antihistamines for children with otitis media.","abstract":"Otitis media is a very common condition in pediatrics and can be quite distressing for children and their parents. Is there a role for antihistamines and decongestants in the management of acute otitis media orotitis media with effusion in children?Traditionally, antihistamines and decongestants have been used in the treatment of otitis media;however, recent guidelines, which are based on study findings with negative results, recommend against routine use. No antihistamine-decongestant combination has been shown to be of clinically significant benefit,and there are potential adverse events that need to be taken into account.","date":"2014-01-23","categories":"Otorhinolaryngologic Diseases","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24452559","annotations":[{"name":"Pediatrics","weight":0.829067,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pediatrics"},{"name":"Adverse effect","weight":0.643556,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Adverse_effect"},{"name":"Therapy","weight":0.617761,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Therapy"},{"name":"Otitis media","weight":0.588317,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Otitis_media"},{"name":"Histamine antagonist","weight":0.548341,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Histamine_antagonist"},{"name":"Statistical significance","weight":0.167804,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Statistical_significance"},{"name":"Otitis","weight":0.113797,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Otitis"},{"name":"Acute (medicine)","weight":0.0551856,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Acute_(medicine)"},{"name":"Effusion","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Effusion"},{"name":"Distressing","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Distressing"},{"name":"Electric charge","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Electric_charge"},{"name":"Mass media","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mass_media"},{"name":"Management","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Management"},{"name":"Decongestant","weight":0.0142619,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Decongestant"}]}
